blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[Coexistence operation] --> B{Channel switch feasible?}
  B -- Yes --> C[Switch channel]
  B -- No --> D{Network assistance?}
  D -- Assisted --> E[RAW sched / beamforming / SST]
  D -- Unassisted --> F[Defer-TX / ED-CCA / Q-learning / change profile]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[共存操作] --> B{可切换信道?}
  B -- 是 --> C[切换信道]
  B -- 否 --> D{需要网络协助?}
  D -- 需协助 --> E[RAW调度 / 波束成形 / SST]
  D -- 不需协助 --> F[延迟发送 / ED-CCA / Q学习 / 改配置]
